    "nameRight": "月咲",
    "textBg": "shout",
    "textRight": "御魂！"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "cheek": 0,
      "eyeClose": 0,
      "face": "mtn_ex_020.exp.json",
      "id": 101700,
      "motion": 0,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_102002/vo_full_102002-6-4",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_102002/vo_full_102002-6-3"
     }
    ],
    "textLeft": "没事，攻击不是冲我来的……"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 101700,
      "motion": 300,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_102002/vo_full_102002-6-5",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_102002/vo_full_102002-6-4"
     }
    ],
    "textLeft": "夏娃和魔女之夜……"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 101700,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_102002/vo_full_102002-6-6",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_102002/vo_full_102002-6-5"
     }
    ],
    "textLeft": "两边的使魔好像在自相残杀呢……"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 101800,
      "motion": 100,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_102002/vo_full_102002-6-7",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_102002/vo_full_102002-6-6"
     },
     {
      "id": 101900,
      "motion": 0
     }
    ],
    "textCenter": "但夏娃的使魔@似乎靠数量占了上风呢。"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 101900,
      "motion": 1,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_102002/vo_full_102002-6-8",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_102002/vo_full_102002-6-7"
     }
    ],
    "textRight": "它们打倒了敌对使魔，@吸收积蓄着它们的污秽……"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 101900,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_102002/vo_full_102002-6-9",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_102002/vo_full_102002-6-8"
     }
    ],
    "textRight": "跟御魂预料的一样呢。"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "cheek": 0,
      "face": "mtn_ex_020.exp.json",
      "id": 101700,
      "motion": 200,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_102002/vo_full_102002-6-10",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_102002/vo_full_102002-6-9"
     }
    ],
    "textLeft": "它们如果只是互相攻击，@那大可这样放着不管，"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 101700,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_102002/vo_full_102002-6-11",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_102002/vo_full_102002-6-10"
     }
    ],
    "textLeft": "但若是还在吸收污秽，@就必须得解决掉它们了……"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "cheek": 0,
      "face": "mtn_ex_001.exp.json",
      "id": 101700,
      "motion": 1,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_102002/vo_full_102002-6-12",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_102002/vo_full_102002-6-11"
     },
     {
      "id": 101800,
      "motion": 0
     },
     {
      "id": 101900,
      "motion": 0
     }
    ],
    "textLeft": "月夜、月咲，"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 101700,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_102002/vo_full_102002-6-13",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_102002/vo_full_102002-6-12"
     }
    ],
    "textLeft": "你们跟别的魔法少女联系上了吗？"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 101900,
      "motion": 100,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_102002/vo_full_102002-6-14",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_102002/vo_full_102002-6-13"
     }
    ],
    "textRight": "嗯，我确认了一下，@她们都在分头行动。"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 101800,
      "motion": 1,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_102002/vo_full_102002-6-15",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_102002/vo_full_102002-6-14"
     },
     {
      "id": 101700,
      "motion": 0
     }
    ],
    "textCenter": "本来是准备在海边迎击魔女之夜的，"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 101800,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_102002/vo_full_102002-6-16",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_102002/vo_full_102002-6-15"
     }
    ],
    "textCenter": "但使魔扩散到了整个城市，@所以她们就分头行动了。"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 101900,
      "motion": 1,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_102002/vo_full_102002-6-17",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_102002/vo_full_102002-6-16"
     }
    ],
    "textRight": "嗯，她们跟我们一样想要击退使魔呢。"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 101700,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_102002/vo_full_102002-6-18",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_102002/vo_full_102002-6-17"
     }
    ],
    "textLeft": "这样呀……"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 101700,
      "motion": 100,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_102002/vo_full_102002-6-19",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_102002/vo_full_102002-6-18"
     }
    ],
    "textLeft": "留在我这边的魔法少女@都出动去对付使魔了，"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "cheek": 0,
      "face": "mtn_ex_010.exp.json",
      "id": 101700,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_102002/vo_full_102002-6-20",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_102002/vo_full_102002-6-19"
     }
    ],
    "textLeft": "那我们就帮她们做后勤吧。"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "cheek": 0,
      "face": "mtn_ex_050.exp.json",
      "id": 101800,
      "motion": 0,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_102002/vo_full_102002-6-21",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_102002/vo_full_102002-6-20"
     },
     {
      "cheek": 0,
      "face": "mtn_ex_050.exp.json",
      "id": 101900,
      "motion": 0
     }
    ],
    "textCenter": "后勤？"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 101700,
      "motion": 1,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_102002/vo_full_102002-6-22",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_102002/vo_full_102002-6-21"
     }
    ],
    "textLeft": "没错。"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 101700,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_102002/vo_full_102002-6-23",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_102002/vo_full_102002-6-22"
     }
    ],
    "textLeft": "我们的工作就是@给各位送去店里的悲叹之种。"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "cheek": 0,
      "face": "mtn_ex_001.exp.json",
      "id": 101700,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_102002/vo_full_102002-6-24",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_102002/vo_full_102002-6-23"
     }
    ],
    "textLeft": "我们一起努力，@为她们提供后勤支援吧。"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 101700,
      "motion": 200,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_102002/vo_full_102002-6-25",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_102002/vo_full_102002-6-24"
     }
    ],
    "textLeft": "还有夏娃的使魔还在筑巢，"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 101700,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_102002/vo_full_102002-6-26",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_102002/vo_full_102002-6-25"
     }
    ],
    "textLeft": "尽管不知道它们有什么目的……@总之先尽量破坏掉吧。"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "cheek": 0,
      "face": "mtn_ex_020.exp.json",
      "id": 101800,
      "motion": 200,
      "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_102002/vo_full_102002-6-27",
      "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_102002/vo_full_102002-6-26"
